FS_ALLOWED_EXTENSIONS=.txt,.json,.xml,.csv,.log,.md,.py,.js,.html,.css
FS_ENABLE_WRITE=true
FS_ENABLE_DELETE=false
FS_MAX_FILE_SIZE=10485760  # 10MB
```

**å¼€å‘ç¯å¢ƒé…ç½®**:
